## The North End: A Study in Persistent Human Habitation

Ah, the [North End](/North_End,_Boston). For those who require such precise geographical coordinates to orient themselves in this fleeting existence, it is a designated [neighborhood](/Neighborhood) nestled within the rather chaotic sprawl of [Boston](/Boston), [Massachusetts](/Massachusetts), United States. A mere speck of land, yet burdened with a history that stretches back to the very dawn of colonial ambition.

